#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:913
msgid "Death of Lédinor"
msgstr "Mort de Lédinor"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:256
msgid "We must not waste any more time, unless we want to be buried alive!"
msgstr ""
"Nous ne devons pas perdre plus de temps ou nous allons finir enterrés "
"vivants !"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:266
msgid ""
"Elynia, it’s over now. There is nothing more for us to do here. We must "
"focus on surviving."
msgstr ""
"Elynia, c'est fini maintenant. Il n'y a plus rien que nous puissions faire "
"ici. Nous devons nous focaliser sur notre survie."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:279
msgid "... I know."
msgstr "... Je le sais bien."

#. [print]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:311
msgid "Checkpoint cleared"
msgstr "Point de contrôle atteint"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:411
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/16_Dawn_of_War.cfg:488
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/10x_Elynia.cfg:208
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23A_Into_the_Lair.cfg:888
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Hein ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:484
msgid "Lava! These tunnels are flooding with lava!"
msgstr "De la lave ! Ces tunnels sont inondés de lave !"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:489
msgid ""
"It’s troubling that I am actually considering the possibility of returning "
"to Inferno to escape this insanity."
msgstr ""
"C'est troublant que je puisse considérer la possibilité de retourner en "
"Inferno pour échapper à cette folie."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:494
msgid ""
"Nonsense! We just must make haste and get to the surface! There ought to be "
"an exit through the hive itself."
msgstr ""
"C'est absurde ! Nous devons juste nous dépêcher de retourner à la surface ! "
"Il doit y avoir une sortie à travers la ruche."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:499
msgid "May I ask if anyone else heard that creature?"
msgstr "Puis-je demander si quelqu'un d'autre a entendu cette créature ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:504
msgid "What creature? Where?"
msgstr "Une créature ? Où ça ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:509
msgid ""
"On the way to this section, in the snow-covered area... It may have been "
"just my imagination, but I believe I heard somebody scream furiously from "
"above."
msgstr ""
"Sur le chemin vers cette section, dans la zone couverte de neige... Ça "
"devait être mon imagination, mais je crois bien avoir entendu quelqu'un "
"hurler furieusement au-dessus de nous."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:561
msgid ""
"Ugh... This is no place for an elder like me. I feel ill. Perhaps it would "
"be best for you if—"
msgstr ""
"Ugh... Ce n'est pas un endroit pour un ancien comme moi. Je me sens mal. "
"Peut-être que ce serait pour le mieux si—"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:566
msgid ""
"<b>NO!</b> ... I mean... I apologize for that, my lord, but I must beg of "
"you to keep going. I don’t want to lose anyone else after all we have been "
"through."
msgstr ""
"<b>HORS DE QUESTION !</b> ... Je veux dire... Pardonnez-moi, mon seigneur, "
"mais je dois vous supplier de continuer. Je ne veux plus perdre personne "
"après tout ce que nous avons traversé."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:571
msgid "... Fair enough. (<i>coughs</i>)"
msgstr "... Fort bien. (<i>tousse</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:580
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/04_Over_the_Sands.cfg:1141
msgid "(<i>coughs</i>)"
msgstr "(<i>tousse</i>)"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:585
msgid "Is something the matter, old elf?"
msgstr "Y a t-il un problème, vieil elfe ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:590
msgid ""
"It’s only getting worse... it feels as if something wanted to burst out of "
"my head. I pray to the Lords of Light that I may survive this ordeal..."
msgstr ""
"Ça ne fait qu'empirer... C'est comme si ma tête allait éclater. Je prie les "
"Seigneurs de Lumière de survivre à ce supplice..."

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:603
msgid "I can’t... continue... Galas, please go on without me..."
msgstr "Je ne peux pas... continuer... Galas, continue sans moi je te prie..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:608
msgid "I refuse, my lord. I—"
msgstr "Je refuse, mon seigneur. Je—"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:613
msgid "<b>ARGH!</b> Galas, please— I— I remember that voice now—"
msgstr ""
"<b>ARGH !</b> Galas, je t'en supplie— Je— Je me souviens de cette voix "
"maintenant—"

#. [message]: speaker=Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:618
msgid "Her voice... She is—"
msgstr "Sa voix... C'est—"

#. [unit]: type=Shadow Courier, id=Corrupted Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:634
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/macros/character-defines.cfg:159
msgid "Lédinor"
msgstr "Lédinor"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:680
msgid "Ehhhhh... yuck. I thought it was only a figure of speech."
msgstr "Oooooh, beurk. Je pensais que c'était seulement une façon de parler."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:685
msgid "What are you?! What did you— What did you do to Lord Léd—"
msgstr "Qu'es-tu donc ? Qu'as-tu fait— Qu'as-tu fait à seigneur Léd—"

#. [message]: speaker=Corrupted Lédinor
#. Corrupted Lédinor is actually Uria remote-possessing his
#. body, so "his" grammatical first person is feminine.
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:692
msgid ""
"You may have escaped to Irdya, but I will <b>not</b> allow you to march away "
"without due punishment for murdering my precious, most loyal vassal!"
msgstr ""
"Vous vous êtes peut-être échappé jusqu'à Irdya, mais je ne vous laisserai "
"<b>pas</b> partir sans punition pour avoir tué le plus précieux, le plus "
"loyal de mes vassaux !"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:697
msgid "Your vassal? Are you... No... It can’t be..."
msgstr "Votre vassal ? Êtes-vous... Non... Cela ne se peut..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:702
msgid ""
"Galas... I fear that no matter what we try, we may never get Lédinor back. "
"Uria must have infected his body in some way before we found him. This is—"
msgstr ""
"Galas... J'ai peur que quoi que nous fassions, nous ne puissions pas "
"récupérer Lédinor. Uria doit avoir infecté son corps d'une façon ou d'une "
"autre avant que nous l'ayons trouvé. C'est—"

#. [message]: speaker=Corrupted Lédinor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:719
msgid ""
"This is only the beginning, Lady of Light. The beginning of your downfall. "
"Everything and everyone you hold dear shall perish in time. I—"
msgstr ""
"Ce n'est que le début, Dame de Lumière. Le début de votre chute. Tout ce qui "
"vous est cher périra bientôt. Je—"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:724
msgid "Take your words to the grave, spawn of Uria!"
msgstr "Emporte tes mots dans la tombe, rejeton d'Uria !"

#. [message]: speaker=Igor
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:736
msgid "That was terrifying... I fear now to think of who’ll be next..."
msgstr "C'était terrifiant... J'ai peur de penser à qui sera le prochain..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:741
msgid ""
"He said he remembered her, Uria... She must have done this to him. It’s the "
"only explanation... the only logical explanation..."
msgstr ""
"Il a dit s'être souvenu d'elle, d'Uria... C'est elle qui a dû lui faire ça. "
"C'est la seule explication... la seule explication logique..."

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:746
msgid ""
"We... really ought to make haste and get out of this dreadful place... lest "
"we find out the exact method Uria uses to possess people like this."
msgstr ""
"Nous... Nous devons vraiment nous hâter de quitter ce terrible endroit... "
"avant de trouver quelle méthode exactement Uria utilise pour posséder les "
"gens de la sorte."

#. [scenario]: id=23C_Broken_Heart
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:798
msgid "Your journey has just begun."
msgstr "Votre voyage ne fait que commencer."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:814
msgid "No! The tunnel is collapsing on us! We weren’t fast enough—"
msgstr ""
"Non ! Le tunnel est en train de s'effondrer sur nous ! Nous n'avons pas été "
"assez rapides—"

#. [unit]: type=Death Knight, id=Lord Azghiel
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:842
msgid "Lord Azghiel"
msgstr "Seigneur Azghiel"

#. [unit]: type=Death Baron, id=Darius
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:855
msgid "Darius"
msgstr "Darius"

#. [unit]: type=Death Baron, id=Durstrag
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:867
msgid "Durstrag"
msgstr "Durstrag"

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Azghiel
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:894
msgid ""
"There they are, the heathens! The Iron Council wants their heads. Get to it!"
msgstr ""
"Ils sont là, ces païens ! Le Conseil de Fer veut leurs têtes. Attrapez-les !"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:899
msgid "(<i>shakes head</i>) Not again..."
msgstr "(<i>secoue la tête</i>) Pas encore..."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:904
msgid ""
"Your emperor has fallen and this fortress is crumbling with him. Flee and "
"get out of our way or we will have to destroy you!"
msgstr ""
"Votre empereur est tombé et cette forteresse est en train de s'effondrer "
"avec lui. Fuyez et dégagez de notre chemin ou nous serons obligés de vous "
"détruire !"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:913
msgid "Keep moving!"
msgstr "Allez, du nerf !"

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:953
msgid "We can’t leave Lord Lédinor behind! We must—"
msgstr "Nous ne pouvons pas laisser Seigneur Lédinor derrière ! Nous devons—"

#. [message]: speaker=Elynia
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:958
msgid "It’s hopeless, Galas... Please, you must understand..."
msgstr "C'est sans espoir, Galas... Je t'en prie, tu dois comprendre..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal Keshar
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:963
msgid ""
"Come on, boy, you ought to know better than this by now, after seeing what "
"became of the Master of Darkness."
msgstr ""
"Allez garçon, tu dois savoir mieux que ça à force, après avoir vu ce qu'il "
"est advenu du Maitre de l'Obscurité."

#. [message]: speaker=Galas
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/23C_Broken_Heart.cfg:972
msgid "I am sorry, my lord. I am so sorry..."
msgstr "je suis désolé, mon seigneur. Je suis sincèrement désolé..."

#. [scenario]: id=05a_Crossfire
#. [part]
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/05a_Crossfire.cfg:5
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/macros/storytxt.cfg:115
