#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/06_The_Moon_Valley.cfg:86
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/06_The_Moon_Valley.cfg:107
#: Invasion_from_the_Unknown/scenarios/15_Shadows_of_Time.cfg:38
